// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4050 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 95a06fdf-988a-5ade-9559-2bc314c9b426

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
